Proteus.Utility.Configuration is a library that abstracts reading config values from e.g., app.config/web.config and supports their being overridden by ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES and/or a local.settings.json files.
summary:
Proteus.Utility.Configuration is a library that abstracts reading config values from e.g., app.config/web.config and supports their being overridden by ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES and/or a local.settings.json file.
	
	This is particularly useful to easily support scenarios such as per-dev settings for dev/test vs. release or per-deployment settings to cloud or otherwise where its necessary to override .config settings on a case-by-base basis.
